headline: A Look At Cboe Global Markets (CBOE) Valuation After Extended RUT Options Trading And Strong Earnings
summary: Why Cboe Global Markets stock is back in focus Cboe Global Markets (CBOE) has drawn fresh attention after rolling out nearly 24 hour trading in Russell 2000 options and reporting fourth quarter and full year 2025 results with higher revenue and earnings. See our latest analysis for Cboe Global Markets. The extended trading hours for Russell 2000 options, solid fourth quarter and full year 2025 results, and a fresh dividend declaration have arrived alongside a 10.9% year to date share price...
